      "raw_text": "Leaders in the movement for\nequal suffrage feel somewhat disap-\npointed over the fact that the SEN\natorial candidates have avoided\nmaking an expression on the ques-\nton. Letter after letter has gone\nto the various candidates for U. S.\nsenator, but none Of them have\ntaken the time to even reply. The\nwomen naturally feel hurt."
